To determine the year of inception of the Association, we can analyze the information provided on the cover page:

*   The title of the document states it is the "Golden Anniversary," which means it is being held fifty years after the Association's inception.
*   The dates mentioned on the cover page are October 2-3, 1956. Since the anniversary is being held in 1956, the Association must have been founded fifty years before that.

Therefore, the year of inception of the Association can be calculated as follows:

*   1956 (year of the anniversary) - 50 (number of years) = 1906

Consequently, the year of inception of the Association is indeed 1906.
